  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MuTA11">
<l>naṉkōtu nālvētat tuḷḷā ṉaṟaviriyum</l>
<l>poṅkō taruvip puṉalvaṇṇaṉ – caṅkōtap</l>
<l>pāṟkaṭalāṉ pāmpaṇaiyiṉ mēlāṉ payiṉṟuraippār</l>
<l>nūṟkaṭalā ṉuṇṇaṟivi ṉāṉ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He is the four Vedas that are well recited, the one of the colour of the torrent</l>
<l>of the foaming, flooding  waterfall in which honey drips , the one of the milk</l>
<l>ocean with conches [and] waves, the one on the snake bed, the one of the sea of</l>
<l>treatises by those of well-trained discourse , the one of subtle knowledge.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
